<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 15:13:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>期待已久的中国政策更新并未出现重大转变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-policy-agenda-with-few-implementation-details-2024-07-21/</link><description>由于中国面临贸易紧张、通货紧缩、房地产危机、债务激增以及消费者和企业信心疲软，一些经济学家希望情况会有所改变。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:02:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-publishes-policy-agenda-with-few-implementation-details-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>马尼拉称，中国和菲律宾就南海补给任务的“临时安排”达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-resupply-ship-south-china-sea-shoal-without-us-help-2024-07-21/</link><description>去年，有争议水道的紧张局势已升级为暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-resupply-ship-south-china-sea-shoal-without-us-help-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>总统表示，台湾必须保护自己的主权，了解自己的历史</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-must-protect-its-sovereignty-know-its-own-history-president-says-2024-07-21/</link><description>周日，台湾总统赖清德表示，台湾必须保护自己的主权，了解自己的文化和历史，他否认了之前关于台湾可以作为“收复”中国的基地的错误看法。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 07:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-must-protect-its-sovereignty-know-its-own-history-president-says-2024-07-21/</guid></item><item><title>英国皮蒂在中国兴奋剂案件后表示，我们需要一个公平的竞争环境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/we-need-level-playing-field-says-britains-peaty-after-chinese-doping-cases-2024-07-20/</link><description>亚当·皮蒂和其他英国游泳运动员表示，23名中国游泳运动员在违禁药物检测呈阳性后逃脱了处罚，需要有一个公平的竞争环境。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 19:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/we-need-level-playing-field-says-britains-peaty-after-chinese-doping-cases-2024-07-20/</guid></item><item><title>公路桥梁垮塌造成11人死亡 习近平敦促全力救援</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-urges-all-out-rescue-efforts-after-highway-bridge-collapse-kills-11-2024-07-20/</link><description>官方媒体称，已确认有 5 辆车落入水中，另有 30 人失踪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 06:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-urges-all-out-rescue-efforts-after-highway-bridge-collapse-kills-11-2024-07-20/</guid></item><item><title>王毅表示，中加应致力于发展战略伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-canada-should-work-toward-strategic-partnership-chinas-wang-says-2024-07-20/</link><description>据外交部称，外交部长王毅对加拿大外长表示，中加应推动关系正常化，重回建立战略伙伴关系的正轨。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 03:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-canada-should-work-toward-strategic-partnership-chinas-wang-says-2024-07-20/</guid></item><item><title>沙利文表示，美国将支持菲律宾为环礁船只补给的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-support-philippines-efforts-resupply-ship-atoll-sullivan-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>白宫国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文周五表示，美国“将采取一切必要措施”，确保菲律宾能够向仁爱礁上的一艘船只提供补给，马尼拉利用这艘船只来加强其对环礁的主权主张。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 20:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-support-philippines-efforts-resupply-ship-atoll-sullivan-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯表示下周将在老挝会见中国外长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-will-see-chinese-counterpart-laos-next-week-2024-07-19/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五表示，他与中国外长通话相当频繁，并补充说他将于下周在老挝见到他。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-says-will-see-chinese-counterpart-laos-next-week-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国行业机构要求欧盟纠正其对电动汽车的调查结果</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-industry-body-tells-eu-correct-its-findings-evs-2024-07-19/</link><description>代表 12 家中国汽车制造商的行业机构在本周的听证会上告​​诉欧盟委员会，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税违反了全球贸易规则，必须予以纠正。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-industry-body-tells-eu-correct-its-findings-evs-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示，特朗普制裁促使小米进入中国电动汽车市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trump-sanctions-prompted-china-xiaomis-ev-entry-ceo-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>小米首席执行官雷军周五表示，特朗普政府于 2021 年初制裁中国小米公司的决定是该公司决定生产首款电动汽车的催化剂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 14:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trump-sanctions-prompted-china-xiaomis-ev-entry-ceo-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将在反倾销调查中对中国生物柴油征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-set-tariffs-chinese-biodiesel-imports-anti-dumping-probe-2024-07-19/</link><description>欧盟发现中国生物柴油以不公平的低价在欧盟市场销售后，将对其征收临时关税，这是一系列针对中国的贸易案件中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 13:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-set-tariffs-chinese-biodiesel-imports-anti-dumping-probe-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国加大对装备升级和消费品以旧换新的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boost-support-equipment-upgrades-consumer-goods-trade-ins-2024-07-19/</link><description>官方媒体周五援引一次内阁会议报道称，中国将加大对设备升级和消费品以旧换新计划的支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 11:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-boost-support-equipment-upgrades-consumer-goods-trade-ins-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：波动性重新出现，技术中断令人烦恼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-19/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官在北京与中国部长讨论贸易和技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-talks-trade-tech-with-chinese-ministers-beijing-2024-07-19/</link><description>根据各部委和大众汽车的声明，大众汽车首席执行官周五在与中国工商部长的会议上讨论了自由和公平贸易、全球经济和技术。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-talks-trade-tech-with-chinese-ministers-beijing-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车CEO：与中国部长讨论自由贸易、全球经济、人工智能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-discussed-free-trade-global-economy-ai-with-chinese-ministers-2024-07-19/</link><description>大众汽车表示，大众汽车首席执行官奥利弗·布鲁姆在周五与中国政府部长的会议上谈到了使用人工智能和自动驾驶等技术的框架条件以及自由和公平贸易的重要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-discussed-free-trade-global-economy-ai-with-chinese-ministers-2024-07-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>